@ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5011

# Authentication Endpoints

### Login as Admin (Alice)
POST {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Regular User (Bob)
POST {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

# User Management (Admin Only)

### Create New User (requires admin token)
POST {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "New User",
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "isAdmin": false
}

###

### Update User (requires admin token)
PUT {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

###

### Delete User (requires admin token)
DELETE {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/users/4
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

# List Management (Authenticated Users)

### Create List (user can only create for themselves unless admin)
POST {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "My New List",
  "ownerID": 2
}

###

### Delete List (only owner or admin)
DELETE {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/lists/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Item Management (Authenticated Users)

### Add Item to List (only list owner or admin)
POST {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/lists/1/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "New Todo Item"
}

###

### Update Item (only list owner or admin)
PUT {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Updated Todo Item"
}

###

### Delete Item (only list owner or admin)
DELETE {{ToDoList.Backend_HostAddress}}/items/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

###
